// SCAFFOLD ONLY — NOT WIRED INTO `make typecheck` or release.yml.
//
// This tsconfig widens the typecheck scope to cover scripts/**,
// bun-build.ts, playwright.config.ts, and tests/** so that type
// regressions in those files can be caught before they manifest at
// runtime (release-pipeline scripts) or during a manual fuzz pass
// (tests/fuzz/**).
//
// Status (2026-04-26): cluster-06 ballpark surfaced 62 type errors
// against this config — too many to fix as part of cluster-06's
// half-day budget (the orchestrator's >20-error branch keeps the
// scaffold landed but unwired). Wiring this into the local Makefile
// typecheck target or the CI Typecheck step would break those gates
// today. See docs/code-analysis/2026-04-26/clusters/06-ci-and-release-improvements.md
// for the cluster context.
//
// First ~10 representative errors from the ballpark run:
//   bun-build.ts(1,22): error TS2305: Module '"bun"' has no exported member 'BuildOptions'.
//   node_modules/electrobun/dist/api/bun/index.ts(32,24): error TS7016: Could not find a declaration file for module 'three'. ...
//   src/client/auth-fetch.ts(49,34): error TS2339: Property '__TMUX_WEB_CONFIG' does not exist on type 'Window & typeof globalThis'.
//   src/client/auth-url.ts(6,61): error TS2339: Property '__TMUX_WEB_CONFIG' does not exist on type 'Window & typeof globalThis'.
//   src/client/colours.ts(68,27): error TS2339: Property '__TMUX_WEB_CONFIG' does not exist on type 'Window & typeof globalThis'.
//   src/client/theme.ts(44,29): error TS2339: Property '__TMUX_WEB_CONFIG' does not exist on type 'Window & typeof globalThis'.
//   src/client/theme.ts(47,7): error TS2322: Type 'ThemeInfo[] | null' is not assignable to type 'ThemeInfo[]'.
//   tests/e2e/helpers.ts(163,5): error TS1117: An object literal cannot have multiple properties with the same name.
//   tests/e2e/session-inheritance.test.ts(7,11): error TS2532: Object is possibly 'undefined'.
//   tests/unit/client/xterm-adapter.test.ts (18 errors): TS2345/TS2322/TS2554 — adapter test fakes drift from current xterm.js types.
//
// Error category counts: TS2345 (19), TS2554 (12), TS2769 (8), TS2339 (8),
// TS2322 (5), TS2493 (3), TS7016 (2), TS2741/TS2739/TS2532/TS2305/TS1117 (1 each).
// (TS5097 is suppressed by `allowImportingTsExtensions: true` below — the
// raw count without that flag was 210.)
//
// To run the gate manually:   bun x tsc --noEmit -p tsconfig.tooling.json
// To wire it into CI:         add the line to release.yml's Typecheck step
//                             AND add it to Makefile:50 (after the 62
//                             errors are driven to zero).
{
  "extends": "./tsconfig.json",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "rootDir": ".",
    "noEmit": true,
    "types": ["node", "bun"],
    "lib": ["ES2022", "DOM", "DOM.Iterable"],
    "allowImportingTsExtensions": true
  },
  "include": [
    "scripts/**/*.ts",
    "bun-build.ts",
    "playwright.config.ts",
    "tests/**/*.ts"
  ],
  "exclude": ["node_modules", "dist", "vendor"]
}
